## **Where This Gets Smart**

Combine multiple probabilities:

```javascript
function recommendSeedWithContext(sectionType, userStyle, currentDetailLevel) {
  const byType = P(seedWorks | sectionType);      // Type match
  const byStyle = P(seedWorks | userStyle);       // User preference
  const byLevel = P(seedWorks | detailLevel);     // Detail interaction

  // Bayesian combination:
  // P(seedWorks | all) ∝ byType × byStyle × byLevel × priorAcceptance

  const combined = bayesianCombine([byType, byStyle, byLevel]);
  return rankSeedsBy(combined);
}
```

